data.description: Don't miss this Tooele Investor Opportunity. Fix and Flip. ARV 600K. This is a perfect opportunity to get an amazing home that needs some work that has the possibility to be a great income producing investment.  Basement has it's own entrance, laundry room and driveway. Basement Kitchen has cabinets and granite countertops just needs to be installed. Main floor was previously beautifully updated with custom cabinets and countertops. This home just needs some TLC with some wall patching, paint and a good cleaning.
